WEBVTT

00:03:57.550 --> 00:04:00.202
We are all deserving of our dignity.

00:04:01.022 --> 00:04:02.789
See yourself in others.

00:04:03.285 --> 00:04:06.269
Recognize that your justice is my justice,

00:04:06.293 --> 00:04:07.885
and mine is yours.

00:04:07.909 --> 00:04:12.821
There can be no liberation for one of us
if the other is not free.

00:04:13.380 --> 00:04:15.703
(Applause)

00:04:16.214 --> 00:04:18.782
The world will say to you,

00:04:18.806 --> 00:04:20.344
"I am violent."

00:04:21.014 --> 00:04:22.850
Respond by saying,

00:04:22.874 --> 00:04:24.055
"I am not.

00:04:24.548 --> 00:04:27.953
Not with my words
and not with my actions."

